Monitor Cluster
   - > Metric Server , Prometheus ,Elastic Stack ,Data Dog, dynatrace ,heapster(Deprecated)
 One metric server for per kubernetess cluster
 Kubelet has one component which name is cAdvisor(container advisor)
 
 minikube addons enable metrics-server
 kubectl top node ->  performance metric for node
 kubectl top pod -> performance metric for pod
 
 Download the kubernetess metric server
  git clone ....
  kubectl create -f .
  
  kubectl logs -f pod
  One pod  can have two container and you you should specified container name 
 
  kubectl logs pod -c <ContainerName>
